reviews: The keyboard has symbols that are for another language and don't have certain symbols that are on a regular keyboard. For example, there is no dollar sign. Frustrating, as this was not on the description.
One bag was stale. It's a great coffee otherwise.
Not super absorbent but no sand stuck to it and easy to pack.

review_title: Ordered a small. but top was too small for anyone with a larger than B cup
reviews: Quality was as expected. Service was great. When I expressed concern over the size of the top, they dealt with it promptly.
The mask doesn't "breathe" at all and caused a skin irritation for my daughter.
The product took way too long to arrive and when we finally received it, it was the wrong product. Very disappointing...
